spec_data.Name: python3-xlrd
spec_data.Description:
Extract data from Excel spreadsheets (.xls and .xlsx, versions 2.0 onwards)
on any platform.  Pure Python (2.6, 2.7, 3.2+).  Strong support for Excel
dates.  Unicode-aware.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 06:59:53 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Library to extract data from Microsoft Excel (TM) spreadsheet files
